company_name: STE COOP DE GESTION ET D ARMENENT DES NAVIRES DE PECHE
information: The company STE COOP DE GESTION ET D ARMENENT DES NAVIRES DE PECHE, founded in 1978, which operates in the Naval construction industry. It also operates in the Fishing vessels - construction industries. It is based in Saint-Gilles-Croix-De-Vie, France.
